        "subject": "LU-7144 tests: print client/server versions for tests",
        "message": "LU-7144 tests: print client/server versions for tests\n\nPrint the client and server versions for sanity-scrub and\nsanity-lfsck so that we can see what they are reporting.\n\nThis is relevant for testing the upstream kernel version,\nsince it appears to be trying to run sanity-scrub and\nsanity-lfsck when it should be skipping them instead, but\nit is useful information to have in general.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <andreas.dilger@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I7b4c5d273883dfc18ab20b43176620842f3ebbe5\n"
      },
